{"tid":2033693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO平權後，如果俾警察非法咁打，會否提升到外交層面事件","createTime":"2020-05-24T21:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:08:37.000Z","uid":149342,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d3fe359be3b3a448d78409c80b11cf38a9ee42c9","tid":2033693,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:07:39.000Z","msg":"英國國民被中國政府欺壓，英國出兵，史稱兩傘戰爭"},{"pid":"bde9222fcc81d796c8b31232b2d5b22446f2543d","tid":2033693,"uid":200083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:08:14.000Z","msg":"首先你係中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc2fb6f92fcdba5203e7052a7da53cbf60e1e94","tid":2033693,"uid":258578,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:10:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5f2e409bfbe6548a8133641df3fc07fcf6289ff","tid":2033693,"uid":165106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ccc2fb6f92fcdba5203e7052a7da53cbf60e1e94","tid":2033693,"uid":258578,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:10:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T21:11:50.000Z","msg":"又係依句呀五毛！"},{"pid":"bb7f5f8e5bf9741683745c6219ee95d663f218a7","tid":2033693,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:08:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok</span></strong>。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請。"},{"pid":"e0e59351e3e51d8d7441701a2ed683b2bb408ec0","tid":2033693,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:08:37.000Z","msg":"BNO平權有助香港建立海外屬地 黃色經濟圈全球化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}